<p>Hi <%= @email %>,</p>

<p>Welcome to Code Nest! Your account is ready &mdash; sign in to set up your workspace, invite your team, and start tracking projects.</p>

<p>
  <%= link_to "Sign in to Code Nest",
        @login_url,
        style: "display:inline-block;padding:10px 16px;background-color:#4f46e5;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;border-radius:6px;font-weight:600;" %>
</p>

<p style="font-size:12px;color:#6b7280;">
  If the button doesn't work, paste this URL into your browser:<br>
  <%= @login_url %>
</p>

<p style="font-size:12px;color:#6b7280;">
  Didn't create a Code Nest account? You can safely ignore this message.
</p>
